            <p>If any provision of these Terms is held invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions will remain in full force and effect. These Terms, together with any signed agreement, constitute the entire agreement between the parties concerning the Services.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>20. Notices and Contact</h2>
            <p>All notices must be sent to:</p>
            <address class="not-italic">
              <strong>Marketing AI Houston</strong><br>
              Email: <a href="mailto:team@marketingaihouston.com">team@marketingaihouston.com</a>
            </address>
          </section>

          <section>
