            <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. Material changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use of the Site or Services after changes indicates acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>
          </section>
        </div>

        <footer class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-ocean-100">
          <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-ocean-600">
            <a href={`${BASE_URL}legal/privacy-policy/`} class="hover:text-ocean-800 underline">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href={`${BASE_URL}legal/cookie-policy/`} class="hover:text-ocean-800 underline">Cookie Policy</a>
            <a href={`${BASE_URL}legal/accessibility-statement/`} class="hover:text-ocean-800 underline">Accessibility Statement</a>
